##  Future Improvements / Roadmap

This project is actively being developed. Planned enhancements include:

###  Conversation Memory
- Persist user chat history using:
  - Local storage (short-term)
  - Database integration (MongoDB / Supabase)
- Enable context-aware responses across multiple messages
- Allow users to revisit previous legal queries

---

### Stop / Refresh Controls
- Add ability to:
  - Stop AI response mid-generation
  - Regenerate (refresh) responses
- Improve user control and interaction experience
- Introduce streaming responses for real-time output

---

###  CanLII API Integration
- Integrate the CanLII API for:
  - Real Canadian case law references
  - Legal document metadata
- Enhance responses with:
  - Case citations
  - Relevant precedents
  - Source-backed legal information

---

###  Backend & Deployment Improvements
- Improve API reliability and error handling
- Add rate limiting and request validation
- Optimize performance for production usage

---

###  Feature Enhancements
- Generate legal documents (e.g., dispute letters)
- Step-by-step legal guidance workflows
- Province-specific legal insights
- Improved prompt engineering for higher accuracy

---

###  Authentication & User Accounts
- Add user login/signup (Firebase / Auth0)
- Save user-specific chat history
- Personalized legal assistance experience

---

###  UI/UX Improvements
- Better loading states and feedback indicators
- Chat response formatting (bullet points, sections)
- Mobile responsiveness optimization

